snippet.title: Portal with N64 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
My brother, Joe Lambert, put this video together as a parody of the recent portal RTX trailer

Latest ROM Download
https://github.com/lambertjamesd/portal64/releases/tag/v0.6.5

N64 Homebrew Resources
https://discord.gg/WqFgNWf
https://n64.dev/#community 

If you want to code using the official N64 SDK
https://crashoveride95.github.io/n64hbrew/modernsdk/index.html

lIf you want to use an open source SDK
https://libdragon.dev/
